<div class="entry">
<div class="content">
The O'Reilly folks have just posted the very-nicely-produced video of my "Reinventing Business" <a href="http://programming.oreilly.com/2014/02/prefer-goals-over-controls.html" target="_blank">presentation</a>. I'm quite pleased with the way it came out and feel like it's a good summary of my progress so far.<div class="blogger-post-footer">-->> Interested in talking about this? Read the "comments" section at 
the bottom of www.reinventing-business.com to learn about joining
the discussion group.</div></div>







<p class="date">
<a href="http://www.reinventing-business.com/2014/02/my-reinventing-business-presentation.html">by noreply@blogger.com (Bruce Eckel) at February 21, 2014 10:02 PM</a>
