<h3><a href="http://alexschroeder.ch/wiki/Diary" title="Alex Schroeder: Diary">Alex Schroeder</a></h3>


<div class="entrygroup" id="http://alexschroeder.ch/wiki/2014-01-27_Nethack_Mapping">
<h4><a href="http://alexschroeder.ch/wiki/2014-01-27_Nethack_Mapping">Nethack Mapping</a></h4>
<div class="entry">
<div class="content">
<p>Today, as we were exploring a ruin of Ianna, I decided I wanted to start mapping on my iPad. But how? Enter ASCII art.</p><pre class="real">▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓
