<h4><a href="http://lambda-the-ultimate.org/node/4876">And the Academy Award goes to... a literate program</a></h4>
<div class="entry">
<div class="content">
<p>Matt Pharr, Greg Humphreys, and Pat Hanrahan have recently been given an Academy Award for Technical Achievement, for the book <a href="http://www.pbrt.org/">Physically Based Rendering</a>. This is the first time the award has been given to a book and (more relevant to LtU) the first time a literate program has won an Academy Award.</p></div>







